## Effort Parameter

Effort is nested inside \`OutputConfig\` \u2014 there is NO \`.effort()\` directly on \`MessageCreateParams.Builder\`.

\`\`\`java
import com.anthropic.models.messages.OutputConfig;

.outputConfig(OutputConfig.builder()
    .effort(OutputConfig.Effort.HIGH)  // or LOW, MEDIUM, MAX
    .build())
\`\`\`

Combine with \`Thinking = ThinkingConfigAdaptive\` for cost-quality control.

